@startuml
title Figure 5.12: Update Job Status Sequence Diagram

actor Administrator
participant "Dashboard Script\n(public/js/script.js)" as Script
participant "API Server\n(src/server.js)" as Api
participant "Orders Store\n(src/orders.js)" as Orders
participant "WhatsApp Client" as WhatsApp
actor Customer

Administrator -> Script : Select new status for order
Script -> Api : PUT /api/orders/:id {status}
Api -> Orders : updateOrder(id, updates)
Orders --> Api : updated order + oldStatus
Api -> Api : compare new status with old status
Api -> WhatsApp : sendMessage(status changed)
WhatsApp --> Customer : Status update message
Api --> Script : success response
Script --> Administrator : Updated dashboard state

@enduml
